title: Straits Settlements and Johore Territorial Waters (Agreement) Act 1928
title_en: Straits Settlements and Johore Territorial Waters (Agreement) Act 1928
description: An Act to approve an Agreement concluded between His Majesty and the Sultan of the State and Territory of Johore.

provisions.title: Approval of Agreement
provisions.content: 1. The approval of Parliament is hereby given to the said Agreement.

provisions.title: Short title
provisions.content: 2. This Act may be cited as the Straits Settlements and Johore Territorial Waters (Agreement) Act 1928.
